title 'Check Your Understanding'

question 'Which of the following situations is MOST likely to trigger a high-risk score and require extra verification?'
wrong 'Logging in from home computer at 8 PM'
right 'Logging in from an unknown device in another country at 3 AM'
wrong 'Opening calendar from school laptop'
wrong 'Using mobile app from familiar location'
allow_multiple_attempts false
